{
  "stem": "2735.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "You know, with some wood, because the old woman-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] I don't remember if we changed places, but she only wanted me to ask because I work in the office and I'll get wood to warm the house.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "All the time I couldn't believe that this is real.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "There was a 15 years old boy there, ugly guy looking.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "If he lived, survived, he probably would've been just like Hitler.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "A sadist, smart, like a whip.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "He knew everything.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And the people now in the whole village, there were the two of us families, and only the member of another family from Russia, from [NON-ENGLISH] who had one son who was a little retarded adult.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And he wasn't taken, because everybody else was taken into the army.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And-- but in the office was a young woman who was-- who came back to her in-laws because she had a baby, and her husband was in the army.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And she was in Rovno the two years when it was next to Russia.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And she was very sweet and very nice.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And we became good friends.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "She invited me to her house, and they lived very good.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "She had very nice silvers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "They were well to do.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "They-- they had underground everything, food and everything else.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "And they told me this story, and it was dressed like a real, prosperous [NON-ENGLISH], those were the landowners.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "And they say that-- I said, I'm surprised that the Communist didn't do anything to them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "He says because his older son was the first to go in the church and break the top, destroy the religion in the village.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "So they respected him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "Make a long story short, the other family didn't have anybody employed.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
